00:02:39.350 --> 00:02:40.870
And what is this
point right here?

00:02:40.870 --> 00:02:45.180
So if we were go all the way
up here, what is that point?

00:02:45.180 --> 00:02:49.120
Well here our x is
3 plus delta x.

00:02:49.120 --> 00:02:50.310
It's the same thing as
this one right here,

00:02:50.310 --> 00:02:50.990
as x naught

