00:02:54.235 --> 00:02:58.110
So it's 3 plus
delta x up there.

00:02:58.110 --> 00:02:59.930
So what's the y
value going to be?

00:02:59.930 --> 00:03:02.080
Well whatever x value is, it's
on the curve, it's going

00:03:02.080 --> 00:03:03.550
to be that squared.

00:03:03.550 --> 00:03:12.310
So it's going to be the point
3 plus delta x squared.

00:03:12.310 --> 00:03:14.790
So let's figure out the
